RELATIONSHIPS - CARDINALITY
 MANAGER manages the BRANCH (1 - N)
 CUSTOMER registers in the respective BRANCH (N – 1)
 CUSTOMER issues BOOKS (1 – N)
 CUSTOMER returns BOOKS (1-N)
 EMPLOYEE updates BOOKS (N – N)
